As RAT TRAP, WINDLORD and PERCEPTOR step on to the shuttle RODIMUS
PRIMAL walked with them, with his much taller form he is having to
bend slightly as he walked through doors and airlocks.

Meawhile the ship itself rumbled and began to lift off.

"We don't have far to go." RODIMUS said as he gestured for the others
to sit down, "But Windlord and Perceptor, tell us what you remember
about your last meeting with these humans. Were there any Predacons
around?"

(TAG)

- Preston
